          <h1>Cozumel special price 4 hour tour</h1>
          <p>Pick you up at your hotel or cruise ship or ferry pier, city tour, visit to Chocolate factory or to Tequila tastings (no tour), 
          visit to San Gervasio Mayan ruins, eastern "wild" side of the island, Palancar Beach for snorkel from shore or have a 
          mexican/seafood lunch, (snorkel gear or food not included), then head back to the hotel or cruiseship for drop off.</p>
     </div>
     
    </div>
