                <li>Four hour taxi private tour (depending on the number of persons) by Taxi Car or Taxi Van with one of our trustworthy and experts drivers/guides</li>
                <li>Choose from a visit to Chocolate tastings at KaoKao Factory or a Tequila tastings at Mexico Lindo</li>
                <li>Entrance fee to San Gervasio Mayan Ruins (guide inside the ruins not included)</li>
